text:
[Verse]
Moon up high light my way
Through the night I wanna play
City lights they start to glow
Dancing feet they steal the show

[Verse 2]
Music loud sky so bright
Feeling free no care in sight
Sidewalks shimmering like gold
Whispers stories yet untold

[Chorus]
Midnight stroll I feel the beat
Every step a rhythmic treat
Hearts in sync we hit the street
Until the dawn we won't retreat

[Verse 3]
Stars above watch us glide
In this moment side by side
Echoes of the night we chase
Lost in our own little space

[Verse 4]
Laughter fills the air we breathe
Night unfolds a magic weave
Holding on to fleeting time
Every note a perfect rhyme

[Chorus]
Midnight stroll I feel the beat
Every step a rhythmic treat
Hearts in sync we hit the street
Until the dawn we won't retreat
title: Midnight Stroll
